file.name: 6016-oas3.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.2
info:
  title: OAS 3.0 sample with entries as property name
  version: 0.1.0
paths:
  /test/:
    get:
      summary: Test
      operationId: test_test__get
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Successful Response
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/Testmodel'
components:
  schemas:
    Testmodel:
      title: Testmodel
      required:
        - name
        - entries
      type: object
      properties:
        name:
          title: Name
          type: string
        entries:
          title: Entries
          type: integer
